---
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const title = "Peter Chapman's Website";
const href = "/";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <article class="wrapper flow">
    <h1 class="full-width">Hi, I'm Peter, a Web Developer Specializing in Building Dynamic Websites</h1>
    <div class="switcher">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-primary">I can build yours, reconfigure it, update, or add to.</h2>
        <p>I have years of experience working with many things web.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Welcome to my space in the web! I'm Peter, and I'm passionate about crafting engaging online experiences through web development. With a keen eye for detail and a knack for problem-solving, I thrive on the challenge of turning ideas into fully functional and visually stunning websites.</p>
        <p>As a web developer, I bring years of experience and expertise to the table. My journey in the world of web development began with a curiosity-driven exploration of coding languages and design principles. Over time, this passion evolved into a career focused on creating dynamic websites that not only meet but exceed the expectations of clients and users alike.</p>
        <p>One of the aspects I love most about web development is its ever-evolving nature. In this fast-paced industry, staying up-to-date with the latest technologies and trends is crucial. Whether it's learning new frameworks, optimizing performance, or embracing responsive design, I'm always eager to learn and adapt to ensure that the websites I build are not just current, but future-ready.</p>
        <p>My approach to web development is rooted in collaboration and communication. I believe that understanding the unique goals and vision of each project is essential to delivering exceptional results. By working closely with clients and stakeholders, I strive to create custom solutions that are tailored to their needs, preferences, and target audience.</p>
        <p>So whether you're a small business looking to establish a strong online presence, a startup in need of a scalable web platform, or an individual with a creative idea itching to come to life, I'm here to help. Let's connect and explore how we can bring your vision to reality in the digital realm. Together, we can build dynamic websites that not only look great but also perform seamlessly across all devices and platforms.</p>
